1:18:52.540 --> 1:18:53.533
- Hello, Clerk.

1:18:54.810 --> 1:18:56.960
Jesus, I've known you for so long

1:18:56.960 --> 1:18:58.633
that I forgot your real name.

1:18:59.730 --> 1:19:00.833
- I forgot myself.

1:19:12.210 --> 1:19:14.900
- Sometimes this island
feels like a prison.

1:19:14.900 --> 1:19:17.040
We certainly behave like prisoners.

1:19:17.040 --> 1:19:20.320
Going by nicknames, dreaming of escaping.

1:19:20.320 --> 1:19:23.385
- Pour vivre heureux, vivons cachés.

1:19:24.218 --> 1:19:26.513
- Yes, to live happy let's live hidden.

1:19:28.160 --> 1:19:29.580
But don't you just wanna
go back to Greatland

1:19:29.580 --> 1:19:32.513
and restore everything
to how it was before?

1:19:33.570 --> 1:19:34.730
We'll drop the act.

1:19:34.730 --> 1:19:37.820
Call ourselves by our
real names and titles.

1:19:37.820 --> 1:19:40.230
Call everything by what it is.

1:19:40.230 --> 1:19:42.350
- You would hold the mirror up

1:19:42.350 --> 1:19:45.570
to the masses of depressed
and neglected people.

1:19:45.570 --> 1:19:47.187
What do you think the result would be?

1:19:47.187 --> 1:19:48.783
- I have no idea.

1:19:50.120 --> 1:19:52.113
But I want real power.

1:19:53.380 --> 1:19:55.353
Not this golden retirement!

1:19:56.210 --> 1:19:59.280
Are you too have this thirst,

1:19:59.280 --> 1:20:02.040
this passion for real impact?

1:20:02.040 --> 1:20:05.010
You want to leave a legacy.

1:20:05.010 --> 1:20:06.800
You and I, we've been waiting

1:20:06.800 --> 1:20:10.390
in the shadow of Alpha
Altruist for decades.

1:20:10.390 --> 1:20:12.093
I've had enough!

1:20:13.040 --> 1:20:14.533
What about you?

1:20:16.970 --> 1:20:18.733
- It won't work.

1:20:19.630 --> 1:20:24.630
We have no resources to
take power in Greatland.

1:20:24.760 --> 1:20:27.570
- You are the smartest
and most competent person

1:20:27.570 --> 1:20:28.800
on this island.

1:20:28.800 --> 1:20:31.450
I'm the voice of Mother.

1:20:31.450 --> 1:20:34.510
Together we can figure it out.

1:20:39.977 --> 1:20:42.450
- We're a dying breed.

1:20:42.450 --> 1:20:44.743
We've been here our entire lives.

1:20:45.880 --> 1:20:48.223
It's too late in the day for escaping.

1:21:00.310 --> 1:21:01.143
- Coward!

1:21:11.980 --> 1:21:15.400
- She thinks that you are
the most competent guy

1:21:15.400 --> 1:21:16.673
on the island!

1:21:18.190 --> 1:21:21.143
And why is no one happy
in a Stone Age marriage?

1:21:21.980 --> 1:21:25.350
- I have a feeling that she's gonna try

1:21:25.350 --> 1:21:27.963
and overthrow the Alpha Altruist.

1:21:29.040 --> 1:21:29.913
- Seriously?

1:21:31.610 --> 1:21:33.390
Well, then why didn't you
take her up on her offer?

1:21:33.390 --> 1:21:35.710
- Because the future of
Greatland will be determined

1:21:35.710 --> 1:21:37.250
by young people

1:21:38.870 --> 1:21:39.983
like you.

1:21:42.270 --> 1:21:45.149
And the strongest amongst them.

1:21:45.149 --> 1:21:47.120
- Don't look at me! I'm not strong.

1:21:47.120 --> 1:21:48.570
- I beg to differ.

1:21:48.570 --> 1:21:50.960
You smashed your bracelet.

1:21:50.960 --> 1:21:54.080
You came to the aid of
a damsel in distress.

1:21:54.080 --> 1:21:55.810
You are a rebel!

1:21:55.810 --> 1:21:58.147
Live with it, embrace it.

1:21:58.147 --> 1:21:59.943
- You really think I'm that dumb?

1:22:01.520 --> 1:22:04.120
You didn't give a shit about
me until you needed me.

1:22:05.220 --> 1:22:07.920
Now you expect me to achieve
everything you failed at.

1:22:09.150 --> 1:22:10.133
Crafty, Dad!

1:22:10.980 --> 1:22:12.123
Real crafty.

1:22:15.920 --> 1:22:16.793
- Yeah, well,

1:22:18.250 --> 1:22:19.083
that's about it.

1:22:23.170 --> 1:22:24.003
- Unbelievable!

1:22:25.890 --> 1:22:28.663
She was right, you are a coward.

1:22:30.370 --> 1:22:32.483
- I'm out! Thanks for the cookies, Dad.

1:22:34.000 --> 1:22:36.143
- Take your emotions out of the equation.

1:22:38.050 --> 1:22:39.363
Think like a Clerk.

1:22:42.060 --> 1:22:42.893
- All right!

1:22:44.833 --> 1:22:47.070
You help me to take Ugly Duck
away from the Alpha Altruist,

1:22:47.070 --> 1:22:48.757
and I'm game to save Greatland.

1:22:51.820 --> 1:22:52.653
Come on!

1:22:54.150 --> 1:22:55.173
Think like a Clerk.

1:22:57.840 --> 1:22:58.673
- Deal.

1:23:04.730 --> 1:23:05.563
- All right.

1:23:06.630 --> 1:23:09.600
Let's find out who's
killing all the Great girls,

1:23:09.600 --> 1:23:11.211
and show them that Clerks have teeth.

1:23:42.919 --> 1:23:44.919
- Is this bug an insect?

1:23:46.740 --> 1:23:47.683
Can it be?

1:23:50.870 --> 1:23:51.703
- Philanthropist,

1:23:51.703 --> 1:23:55.550
the Alpha Altruist wants
to know what happened

1:23:55.550 --> 1:23:58.307
to the last girl he passed on to you.

1:23:59.808 --> 1:24:00.641
- Oh yes!

1:24:01.877 --> 1:24:04.173
The blond beast of prey,

1:24:06.830 --> 1:24:08.363
the magnificent blond beast!

1:24:10.000 --> 1:24:12.860
- Except this one wasn't avidly prowling

1:24:12.860 --> 1:24:15.090
for spoils of victory.

1:24:15.090 --> 1:24:17.560
She was tortured and drowned.

1:24:19.630 --> 1:24:20.463
- Round bugs,

1:24:22.992 --> 1:24:23.909
shiny bugs,

1:24:26.480 --> 1:24:27.313
fat bugs,

1:24:29.250 --> 1:24:30.083
lady bugs.

1:24:33.970 --> 1:24:35.053
I love bugs!

1:24:36.420 --> 1:24:38.210
- He's full blast into bugs.

1:24:38.210 --> 1:24:39.043
- No kidding?

1:24:41.570 --> 1:24:42.763
Philanthropist!

1:24:44.190 --> 1:24:45.813
Who killed the girl?

1:24:47.746 --> 1:24:52.142
- Heaven has no rage

1:24:52.142 --> 1:24:54.913
like love to hatred turned,

1:24:57.000 --> 1:24:58.970
nor hell a fury

1:25:00.640 --> 1:25:02.340
like a woman scorned.

1:25:04.589 --> 1:25:06.089
- "Woman scorned",

1:25:07.250 --> 1:25:09.400
that sounds like the
Alpha Altruist's wife.

1:25:10.670 --> 1:25:14.530
- Ex ore parvulorum veritas.

1:25:16.467 --> 1:25:18.167
- "This child speaks the truth."

1:25:21.020 --> 1:25:23.343
Then Lady Omega has gone bonkers.

1:25:26.630 --> 1:25:28.133
Ugly Duck is in danger.

1:25:30.007 --> 1:25:32.653
Greatland is in danger. We must hurry!

1:25:33.620 --> 1:25:34.470
- Cool bugs, man!

1:26:10.367 --> 1:26:12.433
"To whom it may concern,

1:26:13.350 --> 1:26:15.180
I had killed myself.

1:26:15.180 --> 1:26:19.010
My wife will become the next
Sweetheart of Greatland.

1:26:19.010 --> 1:26:21.747
Take care, the Alpha Altruist."

1:26:23.010 --> 1:26:26.593
- She can't even write
a decent suicide note.

1:26:28.880 --> 1:26:30.713
Ulysses!

1:26:33.531 --> 1:26:35.364
- Time's up Ugly Duck!

1:26:36.634 --> 1:26:37.884
Stupid redhead!

1:26:39.479 --> 1:26:41.229
Die you little whore!

1:26:42.438 --> 1:26:43.271
- Dad?

1:26:43.271 --> 1:26:44.104
- Die now!

1:26:46.322 --> 1:26:48.068
Ugly redhead you!

1:26:48.068 --> 1:26:49.568
- Ulysses help me!

1:26:51.723 --> 1:26:53.993
- Just how fucking dumb is she!

1:26:55.130 --> 1:26:56.933
- No Dad! You could kill Ugly Duck!

1:26:56.933 --> 1:26:58.233
I have to go and save her!

1:27:03.681 --> 1:27:06.048
Not my Mother, not my Sweetheart.

1:27:10.116 --> 1:27:10.949
Fuck!

1:27:23.986 --> 1:27:25.683
- I'm so sorry, Ulysses!

1:27:27.560 --> 1:27:29.032
You were right!

1:27:29.032 --> 1:27:30.760
Alpha Altruist tried to contaminate me

1:27:30.760 --> 1:27:33.040
with his Life Force when his wife.

1:27:33.040 --> 1:27:34.033
- Small wonder

1:27:35.829 --> 1:27:39.593
that Trojans and Achaeans endured so much

1:27:40.880 --> 1:27:41.893
and for so long,

1:27:43.000 --> 1:27:46.173
for the sake of a woman so
marvelously and divinely lovely.

1:27:48.070 --> 1:27:49.527
- You read the "Odyssey"!

1:28:04.890 --> 1:28:05.723
- Gotcha!

1:28:10.680 --> 1:28:12.397
- She's heading to Greatland.

1:28:13.690 --> 1:28:16.870
Our self-proclaimed Sweetheart needs TV

1:28:16.870 --> 1:28:18.023
to make herself legit.

1:28:18.940 --> 1:28:19.840
- How do you know?

1:28:21.300 --> 1:28:23.850
- That's the advantage
of spending your life

1:28:23.850 --> 1:28:25.513
in the shadows of power.

1:28:26.360 --> 1:28:27.370
Plenty of time

1:28:28.530 --> 1:28:29.893
to observe,

1:28:32.012 --> 1:28:35.000
to learn

1:28:38.278 --> 1:28:39.278
and prepare.

1:28:49.460 --> 1:28:50.993
- My fellow Greats!

1:28:52.290 --> 1:28:53.537
The time has come.

1:28:55.670 --> 1:28:59.700
According to the Tokens of
Love cast for both candidates,

1:28:59.700 --> 1:29:02.167
the next Greatland's Sweetheart is

1:29:05.380 --> 1:29:06.213
I'm nervous,

1:29:10.135 --> 1:29:11.644
Jörg Doberman!

1:29:11.644 --> 1:29:13.061
- Let's go champ!

1:29:19.628 --> 1:29:21.176
- A dog again?!

1:29:21.176 --> 1:29:24.737
- No loving way! Fraud! Rigged! Boo!

1:29:24.737 --> 1:29:26.531
- Felinist goddesses!

1:29:26.531 --> 1:29:28.114
Join my Revolution!

1:29:37.192 --> 1:29:38.609
- I'm your Mother

1:29:39.677 --> 1:29:43.893
and I proclaim myself the
Greatland's Sweetheart!

1:29:47.360 --> 1:29:48.520
- Who the love is this?

1:29:48.520 --> 1:29:50.968
- Another one of those crazy Felinists!

1:29:50.968 --> 1:29:52.580
- I'm so confused right now

1:29:52.580 --> 1:29:53.930
it's making me lose weight.

1:29:55.200 --> 1:29:57.446
- My dear Great children!

1:29:57.446 --> 1:29:59.200
I'm your Mother.

1:29:59.200 --> 1:30:01.120
Don't listen to this woman.

1:30:01.120 --> 1:30:04.353
She's an anti-Felinist hate-monger.

1:30:05.240 --> 1:30:06.860
- Not my Sweetheart!

1:30:06.860 --> 1:30:09.790
I'm not her! I'm who I
am and I deserve better!

1:30:09.790 --> 1:30:12.920
- Try soul-crushing pain and
devastation and hopelessness

1:30:12.920 --> 1:30:14.730
to describe how we are
feeling in this moment.

1:30:14.730 --> 1:30:17.513
- No! Greats won't be silenced!

1:31:01.030 --> 1:31:02.380
My children!

1:31:02.380 --> 1:31:04.020
As your Mother,

1:31:04.020 --> 1:31:08.440
I'm appalled and saddened to
inform you that this morning,

1:31:08.440 --> 1:31:12.000
Jörg Doberman was cowardly
put out for Resurrection

1:31:12.000 --> 1:31:15.623
by this fanatic Felinist woman.

1:31:18.610 --> 1:31:19.450
- Didn't we just say.

1:31:19.450 --> 1:31:20.953
- Shush!

1:31:20.953 --> 1:31:22.820
Everything you're saying now

1:31:22.820 --> 1:31:25.800
is being broadcast across Greatland.

1:31:25.800 --> 1:31:28.510
- But didn't we just say
she was anti Felinist,

1:31:28.510 --> 1:31:31.160
and now we're saying she
is a Felinist fanatic!

1:31:31.160 --> 1:31:32.890
- It doesn't matter.

1:31:32.890 --> 1:31:34.590
Mother can say whatever she wants.

1:31:38.350 --> 1:31:40.443
- Clerk! Open up! We know you're there!

1:31:44.062 --> 1:31:46.340
- Enough is enough!

1:31:46.340 --> 1:31:48.007
Down with Felinists!

1:32:05.740 --> 1:32:07.860
- We're here on the order of Lady Omega.

1:32:07.860 --> 1:32:09.460
Release the hostage immediately!

1:32:10.940 --> 1:32:12.759
- What hostage?

1:32:17.380 --> 1:32:18.873
Is it what I think?

1:32:25.080 --> 1:32:25.913
- What?!

1:32:25.913 --> 1:32:27.323
I found her on the floor.

1:32:36.030 --> 1:32:37.650
- Unrest is spreading.

1:32:37.650 --> 1:32:39.097
We need to deploy the Optimists.

1:32:39.097 --> 1:32:40.740
- No way! This is fun!

1:32:40.740 --> 1:32:42.291
- This is not a joke Ulysses!

1:32:43.210 --> 1:32:44.610
- Clerk! Don't make me do it!

1:32:44.610 --> 1:32:46.610
- We're losing control of the situation!

1:32:48.590 --> 1:32:50.590
- Greatland is one big scam!

1:32:50.590 --> 1:32:51.650
No one cares.

1:32:51.650 --> 1:32:52.780
No one tells the truth.

1:32:52.780 --> 1:32:55.390
No one should be in charge of this mess.

1:32:55.390 --> 1:32:57.023
Let it all blow to pieces!

1:32:59.260 --> 1:33:01.123
- Is this how we kill each other?

1:33:02.420 --> 1:33:03.953
Ulysses, this is scary.

1:33:05.520 --> 1:33:07.173
How do we go back?

1:33:08.272 --> 1:33:10.650
In our "Amazing Love Store

1:33:10.650 --> 1:33:13.050
when something was broken, we'd fix it.

1:33:13.050 --> 1:33:15.848
Dad would never let us throw it away.

1:33:15.848 --> 1:33:17.143
I want my Greatland back.

1:33:19.330 --> 1:33:22.220
Please, make this madness stop.

1:33:22.220 --> 1:33:24.340
- The majority of Greats
are feeling the same way,

1:33:24.340 --> 1:33:26.250
I guarantee you they're scared.

1:33:26.250 --> 1:33:28.050
- Clerk! You're a dead man!

1:33:28.050 --> 1:33:32.060
- Ulysses, you came here as Nobody.

1:33:32.060 --> 1:33:33.133
Now you have Duck.

1:33:34.050 --> 1:33:36.793
Together, you are Everybody.

1:33:39.087 --> 1:33:41.670
- And what does Everybody want?

1:35:22.140 --> 1:35:25.050
My children, Greats don't hate.

1:35:25.050 --> 1:35:26.370
We love.

1:35:26.370 --> 1:35:28.370
No need to fight.

1:35:28.370 --> 1:35:31.230
I, your Mother, will make sure that sons

1:35:31.230 --> 1:35:34.470
of Jörg Doberman grow
strong and will compete

1:35:34.470 --> 1:35:37.990
for the Greatland's Sweetheart
title in the near future.

1:35:37.990 --> 1:35:41.080
By love, we live forever!

1:35:41.080 --> 1:35:43.240
Meanwhile, Cat Purry will act

1:35:43.240 --> 1:35:45.393
as Greatland's Interim Sweetheart.

1:35:52.220 --> 1:35:54.270
- Phew, what a scare!

1:35:54.270 --> 1:35:57.140
But all's well that ends well.

1:35:57.140 --> 1:36:00.020
All love and admire Cat Purry!

1:36:00.020 --> 1:36:03.585
- All love and admire Cat Purry!

1:36:03.585 --> 1:36:06.520
- The new Greatland Sweetheart!

1:36:06.520 --> 1:36:09.295
- The new Greatland Sweetheart!

1:36:09.295 --> 1:36:12.128
- Greatland! Greatland! Greatland!

1:36:26.923 --> 1:36:28.020
- Clerk! We're breaking in!

1:36:30.450 --> 1:36:33.357
- All right, time's up.

1:37:10.535 --> 1:37:11.368
- Come on!

1:37:27.850 --> 1:37:29.760
- Why did you blow up
the House on the Hill?

1:37:29.760 --> 1:37:31.140
I thought you were all for continuity!

1:37:31.140 --> 1:37:32.023
- I snapped.

1:37:35.680 --> 1:37:39.180
I owe your Father a great debt.

1:37:39.180 --> 1:37:40.513
This is for you,

1:37:41.633 --> 1:37:43.693
a small token of my gratitude.

1:37:45.200 --> 1:37:46.470
- Thank you, Uncle Clerk.

1:37:46.470 --> 1:37:48.450
- With the House on the Hill gone,

1:37:48.450 --> 1:37:50.950
this is the only thing
that commands the Optimists

1:37:51.870 --> 1:37:53.877
and pretty much everything in Greatland.

1:37:56.660 --> 1:37:58.210
You are Mother now.

1:37:58.210 --> 1:38:01.067
- Uncle Clerk, you mean so much to me.

1:38:04.833 --> 1:38:07.295
- Clerk! It's over! Give up Cat Purry!

1:38:12.157 --> 1:38:14.330
- Get to the boat! They won't
follow you to the mainland.

1:38:14.330 --> 1:38:16.910
They're shit scared of Greats.

1:38:16.910 --> 1:38:18.077
- No, I'm not leaving you!

1:38:18.077 --> 1:38:19.513
- Listen to me, Clerk.

1:38:20.660 --> 1:38:24.490
Rule Greatland in Cat Purry's name.

1:38:24.490 --> 1:38:27.540
Open the minds of the Greats gradually.

1:38:27.540 --> 1:38:31.640
No chaos, no brisk
moves, smooth transition.

1:38:31.640 --> 1:38:34.680
Study the Mind Map, it has many levels.

1:38:34.680 --> 1:38:37.910
Find the blueprint for the
Great Reform and follow it.

1:38:37.910 --> 1:38:39.073
- Please, come with me!

1:38:40.470 --> 1:38:42.560
- This island's all I know.

1:38:42.560 --> 1:38:44.963
I am a coward, Ulysses.

1:38:46.080 --> 1:38:47.880
I wouldn't last a day in a new world.

1:38:47.880 --> 1:38:49.418
- Ulysses hurry up!

1:38:51.210 --> 1:38:53.951
- By love, we live forever! Now go!

1:38:53.951 --> 1:38:55.001
Ulysses!

1:38:58.888 --> 1:38:59.721
- Hey!

1:39:00.787 --> 1:39:01.620
Hey!

1:40:07.430 --> 1:40:08.823
- Be strong saith my heart.

1:40:11.130 --> 1:40:12.020
I am a Clerk.

1:40:46.970 --> 1:40:50.920
There will be killing
until the score is paid.
